data.description: Welcome to this charming single-story home located in the Morgans Landing subdivision of Alvin, TX. This beautifully designed residence boasts four spacious bedrooms and two bathrooms. As you enter, you are greeted by an inviting living and dining area. The open-concept layout seamlessly connects the living and dining room to the adjacent kitchen, featuring an eat-in breakfast area and ample counter space. The bedrooms provide comfort and privacy, with one room offering the flexibility to be used as a home office/study. The backyard is a serene retreat with no back neighbors. Located on a cul-de-sac, this home offers easy access to local amenities, schools, and transportation. There have been multiple updates made-including a new roof and fence (2023) and a new HVAC system (2022). Don't miss this opportunity to make this meticulously maintained home your own! Open Houses scheduled for 6/17/23 and 6/18/23
